criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Potential renal donors with no known renal disease (initial medical screening
             performed and scheduled for further imaging evaluation as renal donor);

          -  Age 18-65 years;

          -  No medications (birth control pills and vitamins are acceptable).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Age <18 years or >65 years;

          -  MRI contrast allergy, general contraindications to MRI such as pacemaker, etc.
